entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: The hostages' location has been found! You traveled to a cave in the mountains near Doaba Guerfel. Free the kidnapped victims!
entries.journal_entry_description: Another kidnapping has occurred. Try to locate where these people are.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Another group of people disappeared. Go to their last known location.
entries.task00_journal_entry_title: Find the Spot Where the Others Disappeared
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Looks like a small group of hunters remained at the location to cover the tracks.
entries.task02_comm_message_text: One had a communicator. We have antennae in the area and will be able to track that signal. I need you to activate those antennae and add in the coordinates.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: One had a communicator. We have antennae in the area and will be able to track that signal. I need you to activate those antennae and add in the coordinates.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Go to the first antenna, activate it and input the signal frequency.
entries.task04_comm_message_text: Good. Activate the next two signals.
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: Good. Activate the next two signals.
entries.task05_journal_entry_description: Go to the second antenna, activate it and input the signal frequency.
entries.task06_comm_message_text: I should be able to triangulate the signal once you get the third antenna working.
entries.task06_journal_entry_description: I should be able to triangulate the signal once you get the third antenna working.
entries.task07_journal_entry_description: Go to the third antenna, activate it and input the signal frequency.
entries.task08_comm_message_text: I have the signal! Great work. Follow the coordinates and see what's there.
entries.task08_journal_entry_description: I have the signal! Great work. Follow the coordinates and see what's there.
entries.task09_journal_entry_description: You have a location where the signal originates. Go there.
entries.task09_journal_entry_title: Go to the Signal's Origination Point
entries.task10_journal_entry_description: You need to get into the cave. Kill the guards.
entries.task11_comm_message_text: Listen, they know that they are in trouble. A transmission just came from there threatening to kill their hostages. Do whatever you must to save them. I'll transfer all the information that I have to you.
entries.task11_journal_entry_description: Listen, they know that they are in trouble. A transmission just came from there threatening to kill their hostages. Do whatever you must to save them.
